{"tid":629161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先阿妹畫畫","createTime":"2018-04-14T13:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T10:37:58.000Z","uid":79005,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1f190026ba35db72fb1afce77b7da3c8973cace4","tid":629161,"uid":79005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:04:40.000Z","msg":"我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   阿妹：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/204236_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F204236_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b57a2460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇下我幅畫畫得靚唔靚吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 幾靚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咦？上面嗰幾隻係咩字黎㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :係龜兔賽跑吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我唔識寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我寫比你睇吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咦？ 下面右手邊果隻咩黎㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 龜兔賽跑有獅子嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：我唔識畫烏龜啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以咪畫隻獅子頂住檔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企咪有五隻龜 照住畫咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 阿哥 我有試過嫁  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過D烏龜喺我畫嗰陣成日郁嚟郁去 搞到我畫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我笑左勁耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又答唔到佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係讚佢乖  比着你地會點覆 連登仔請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93ee39945b01844923bc9fe09bcab4f582fdd9b","tid":629161,"uid":29929,"like":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"咁你試下睇下我隻大龜囉<br />\n<br />\n唔會亂郁，但會不斷變大"},{"pid":"5adfa1cdc2b8216558ae07185c4e7e7d5ed33f0e","tid":629161,"uid":36478,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a90818477684d2d2f9911bd6233e0962d8e2b89","tid":629161,"uid":34942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93ee39945b01844923bc9fe09bcab4f582fdd9b","tid":629161,"uid":29929,"like":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"咁你試下睇下我隻大龜囉<br />\n<br />\n唔會亂郁，但會不斷變大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:08:28.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀 個龜頭仲好似你添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f966e200e09aa620caeafc2ac652804aa8c1a9e","tid":629161,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a90818477684d2d2f9911bd6233e0962d8e2b89","tid":629161,"uid":34942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93ee39945b01844923bc9fe09bcab4f582fdd9b","tid":629161,"uid":29929,"like":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"咁你試下睇下我隻大龜囉<br />\n